version_description: We fine-tuned the logarithmic scale of the launch progress that caused space pods to be placed on a fuel tank if you gathered them all. That caused a malfunction in the code. We are deeply sorry, but download this update and say ”bazoom, bazoom” and it’ll start working again!

We fine-tuned the logarithmic scale of the launch progress that caused space pods to be placed on a fuel tank if you gathered them all. That caused a malfunction in the code. We are deeply sorry, but download this update and say ”bazoom, bazoom” and it’ll start working again!

◉ Buildings on planets as you colonize!
◉ 10 new capsules that are on the edge of coolness.
◉ Generate young astronauts straight from the training center!
◉ New Dead Astronauts leaderboards!
◉ Spin the planets after landing!
◉ Don't miss a beat... We help you on that.
◉ John Watt's telescope has seen something?
◉ Camera man was fired since he couldn't follow rockets precisely. Now we have AI to follow rockets. That is progress!
